@Mojo(name="dependency-updates-aggregate-report", requiresDependencyResolution=RUNTIME, threadSafe=true, aggregator=true) public class DependencyUpdatesAggregateReportMojo extends AbstractDependencyUpdatesReportMojo
Generates an aggregate report of available updates for the dependencies of a project.
